txt.en: Ost Dunhoth is an ancient Gondorian fortress in Enedwaith. The Gaunt-lord Gortheron has claimed it as the base of his power.

Ost Dunhoth is an ancient Gondorian fortress, corrupted by the Gaunt-lord Gortheron for his foul and dark uses.
